    • Method Detail

      • init

        public void init()
        The following function initializes the player's attributes at the beginning of the game and displays his money, location and name. If there are players 5 and 6, their attributes are also initialized.

      • updatePlayer

        public void updatePlayer()
        The following function allows you to update the information of each player in the player list bar. It mentions which player is currently playing, the counter associated with the player, his money, his rental, and his current loan. It also indicates if the player is in jail or has lost the game.

      • transferController

        public void transferController​(FieldController main)
        Sets the parent controller to the given controller
        Parameters:
        main - the new parent controller of this controller
